WEBVTT

00:08:59.428 --> 00:09:00.829
You see, after three years

00:09:00.853 --> 00:09:04.091
of my four-and-a-half-year
commandship in that district,

00:09:04.115 --> 00:09:05.269
three years in,

00:09:05.293 --> 00:09:07.972
after putting pastors
in the car with my police

00:09:07.996 --> 00:09:10.171
because I knew this --
it's a little secret --

00:09:10.195 --> 00:09:11.354
I knew this:

00:09:11.378 --> 00:09:14.043
it was hard to stay a nasty police officer

00:09:14.067 --> 00:09:16.168
while you're riding around
with a clergy.

00:09:16.192 --> 00:09:18.374
(Laughter)

00:09:18.398 --> 00:09:24.195
(Applause)

00:09:26.476 --> 00:09:30.005
You'd be getting in and out of the car,
looking to your right, talking about: